# ============================================================
# TURKEY OIS POLICY PRICER — V2
# Short-end, meeting-step, trader-focused rebuild
# ============================================================
#
# Run All in Bloomberg BQuant.
#
# What the model does
# -------------------
# 1. Uses only 1W–1Y TRY OIS quotes.
# 2. Converts each short OIS quote into a discount factor.
# 3. Interpolates LOG DISCOUNT FACTORS smoothly between quoted maturities.
# 4. Fits a PIECEWISE-CONSTANT overnight-rate path whose jumps occur only on
#    scheduled CBRT meeting dates.
# 5. Maps the overnight path to a policy-equivalent path using an explicit
#    overnight-policy basis.
# 6. Lets the user edit meeting moves and reprices one selected OIS trade.
#
# The curve is smooth; the policy path is stepwise.
# ============================================================

